rows.label: tlk45300071_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I overheard the soldiers discussing
something about Superbia and Invidia.

rows.label: tlk45300071_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm Superbian myself, but I'm not
too thrilled with the way our military
goes about things.

rows.label: tlk45300071_02_msg0003
rows.name:
That refugee camp's full of people who
lost their homes in the territorial war
Superbia waged on Gula, isn't it?

rows.label: tlk45300071_02_msg0004
rows.name:
All I can do is stand here tossing
money down and praying for peace.
